CBRE are pleased to present to the market, this office warehouse in a prime Canning Vale location.

Property features:
- Undercover loading and unloading
- Full site circulation
- Excellent on site parking
- Dual crossovers
- Suitable for a wide range of uses
- Clear span warehouse

Improvements:
- Office 285sqm*
- Warehouse 1,979sqm*
- Mezzanine 116sqm*

This property represents an excellent opportunity for a tenant to occupy a very well designed low maintenance office-warehouse located next to Roe Highway

CBRE are pleased to offer for lease this office warehouse accommodation.

Almost new quality Office Warehouse premises with single roller door and high exposure on Baile Road.

The property is situated 17km* to Perth CBD, 15km* to Perth international Airport and 23km* to Port Fremantle. Easy access to Kwinana Freeway and Roe Highway along with other arterial roads.

586sqm* of improvements including 46sqm* of office/amenities and 540sqm* of first class warehouse. The warehouse has a truss height of 8-9 metres* and single front roller door access.

*approx

CBRE are pleased to offer for lease a quality Office Warehouse premises with dual roller door and high exposure on Baile Road.

The property is situated 17km* to Perth CBD, 15km* to Perth international Airport and 23km* to Port Fremantle. Easy access to Kwinana Freeway and Roe Highway along with other arterial roads.

1,125sqm* of improvements including 282sqm* of office/amenities and 843sqm* of first class warehouse. The warehouse has a truss height of 8-9 metres* and twin roller door access.

The building has a total site area of 1,957sqm*.

Centrally located within Canning Vale and close to Roe Highway.

Excellent on site parking.
